text: Anyone used the test recorder in preview 3 of AS? Any impressions?
<@U09T8SFG8>: tried, didn’t find it that useful but might be soon

<@U09T8SFG8> I tried it.  It works as I had expected however they will have to keep adding functionality for it to be useful.  Some of the frustrations at the moment is that a test recording session = a test case where I would like to have multiple sessions in on class.  Also the assertion to is cool but doesn’t allow you do things like check error text on textbox.  I am happy that they are creating it though
